{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/phpNginxCI_1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ol>\n<li>PHP + Nginx 개발 환경 설정</li>\n<li>Nginx 이해</li>\n<li>PHP 언어 사용방법 학습</li>\n<li>Codeigniter를 사용한 MVC 구현 방법 학습</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"1-window--linux-환경-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-window--linux-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"1 window  linux 환경 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Window / Linux 환경 설정</h1>\n<p><strong>아파치와 php7는 라이브러리 충돌 및 오류 때문에 잘 쓰이지 않음</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"window-php-환경-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#window-php-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"window php 환경 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Window PHP 환경 설정</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>WNMP 설치</li>\n<li>{설치경로}/conf/nginx/nginx.conf - root directory 변경 </li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"linux-환경-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#linux-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"linux 환경 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Linux 환경 설정</h2>\n<p>환경 설정 방법</p>\n<ol>\n<li>PHP-fpm 실행</li>\n<li>nginx 실행</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> nginx\nNginx 실행 <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> nginx start \nNginx 중단 <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> nginx stop \nNginx 재시작 <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> nginx restart  / nginx 서버 중단 후 재가동\nNginx 리로드 <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> nginx reload  / 설정만 다시 적용\nNginx 자동 시작 <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> nginx <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">enable</span> \nNginx 상태 <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> nginx status</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>php 설치</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> php-fpm</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>/etc/nginx/sites-available/default 파일 수정</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1. index.php 자동 인식하게 설정\nindex index.html index.htm index.nginx-debian.html;\n\n2. 설치한 php fpm에 맞게 수정\nlocation ~ \\.php$ {\n  include snippets/fastcgi-php.conf;\n  fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php/php7.2-fpm.sock\n}\n\n3. 원하는 root경로 설정\nroot /{원하는 경로}</code></pre></div>\n<p>간단하게 index.php 파일을 만들어 들어가봤다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">phpinfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4c757bee126c21797a219568d00ccc5/58bb7/phpinfo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 94.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"phpinfo\"\n        title=\"phpinfo\"\n        src=\"/static/f4c757bee126c21797a219568d00ccc5/fcda8/phpinfo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f4c757bee126c21797a219568d00ccc5/12f09/phpinfo.png 148w,\n/static/f4c757bee126c21797a219568d00ccc5/e4a3f/phpinfo.png 295w,\n/static/f4c757bee126c21797a219568d00ccc5/fcda8/phpinfo.png 590w,\n/static/f4c757bee126c21797a219568d00ccc5/efc66/phpinfo.png 885w,\n/static/f4c757bee126c21797a219568d00ccc5/58bb7/phpinfo.png 985w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"tip\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tip\" aria-label=\"tip permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Tip!!</strong></h2>\n<p>설정파일 이상 여부 검사 </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nginx -t</code></pre></div>\n<p>error log확인 </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">tail</span> -f /var/log/nginx/error.log  </code></pre></div>\n<p>텍스트 모드 부팅 설정 (더 빨라짐)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> systemctl set-default multi-user.target</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://m.blog.naver.com/skddms/220575084716\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">putty로 virtualbox 연결하기 - 숭숭이님 블로그</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://hyoje420.tistory.com/51\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">[Vim]vim 설정하기 - heyhyo님 블로그</a>  </p>","excerpt":"PHP + Nginx 개발 환경 설정 Nginx 이해 PHP 언어 사용방법 학습 Codeigniter를 사용한 MVC 구현 방법 학습 1. Window / Linux 환경 설정 아파치와 php7는 라이브러리 충돌 및 오류 때문에 잘 쓰이지 않음 Wi…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/ph